  playerStats: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b7d3c9e7f6c33844e81cb8cbf5f34e55, type: 2}
  title: The main plaza of the Ocularium is the most crowded square in the district.
    It may not be the most glamorous venue, but we shall ensure the greatest number
    of commoners lay eyes upon it.
  description: 'COST: 20 Flock'
